ue\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tqa1665703220633.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tqa1665703220633.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tqa1665703220633.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tqa1665703220633\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$CHECK_BOX\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the video attributes for a check box in character mode.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__topic_d139601e1_d139602e1_d139603e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__p_d139604e1_d139605e1_d139606e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$CHECK_BOX</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Selected</var>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Cleared</var>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>{ <var class=\"keyword varname\">Undetermined</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__section_ndp_5zt_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d977540e79\"> Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__p_d142763e1_d142764e1_d142765e1\">Each argument specifies one or more video attribute\n        codes. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lsj1665702873847.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsj1665702873847.html\" title=\"Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences.\">Video Attributes</a>. To define more than one\n        video attribute for each argument, separate them with commas and enclose them in\n        parentheses.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__section_rst_wzt_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d977540e95\"> Defaults </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__table_d16646e1_d16647e1_d16648e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> client assignment files </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> [SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__section_gzr_zzt_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d977540e141\"> Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__p_d139619e1_d139620e1_d139621e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$CHECK_BOX</span> determines the video attributes for each state of a check box\n        in character mode, that is, when the check box is selected or cleared, and, for a tri-state\n        check box, undetermined.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__p_d139622e1_d139623e1_d139624e1\">The default setting for a check box in character mode\n        is:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__pre_k2y_115_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$CHECK_BOX = ,,INV</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__section_opx_b15_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle exampletitle\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__p_d139625e1_d139626e1_d139627e1\"> Example: $CHECK_BOX\n      </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__p_d139628e1_d139629e1_d139630e1\">For each check box state, the following setting\n        displays the check box with the following appearance:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__ul_vrn_d15_1wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__li_d49523e1_d49524e1_d49525e1\">Selected—blinking purple character on a white\n          background (40 + 7) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__li_d49526e1_d49527e1_d49528e1\">Cleared—unblinking purple letters on a white\n          background </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__li_d49529e1_d49530e1_d49531e1\">Undetermined—unblinking purple letters on a white\n          background </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"tqa1665703220633__pre_wrn_d15_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$CHECK_BOX = (BLI,COL=47), COL=47, UND</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsj1665702873847.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Video Attributes</a><p>Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxi1688449052174.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ucheckbox (CheckBox)</a><p>The ucheckbox widget enables the user to set a Boolean value in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called CheckBox, which is mapped to ucheckbox.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532470\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532470\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$CHECK_BOX Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $CHECK_BOX Set the video attributes for a check box in character mode. $CHECK_BOX { = } { Selected } , { Cleared } , { Undetermined } Arguments Each argument specifies one or more video attribute codes. For more information, see Video Attributes . To define more than one video attribute for each argument, separate them with commas and enclose them in parentheses. Defaults Assignment file: client assignment files Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description $CHECK_BOX determines the video attributes for each state of a check box in character mode, that is, when the check box is selected or cleared, and, for a tri-state check box, undetermined. The default setting for a check box in character mode is: $CHECK_BOX = ,,INV Copy Example: $CHECK_BOX For each check box state, the following setting displays the check box with the following appearance: Selected—blinking purple character on a white background (40 + 7) Cleared—unblinking purple letters on a white background Undetermined—unblinking purple letters on a white background $CHECK_BOX = (BLI,COL=47), COL=47, UND Copy Related Links Video Attributes Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences. ucheckbox (CheckBox) The ucheckbox widget enables the user to set a Boolean value in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called CheckBox, which is mapped to ucheckbox. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}